Get Your Mind and Body Ready for Fifty Shades Darker With These Sexy New Photos 
How many ways can Christian Grey do smouldering? Most Popular By Peggy Truong Feb 3, 2017 To mark the one-week countdown to the release of Fifty Shades Darker , Universal Pictures has blessed with world with new official stills from the film. They're sexy, they're beautiful, and yes, they're even dark. The photos arrive one day after the film held its Hollywood premiere at the Ace Hotel, with Dakota Johnson stepping out in Valentino and Jamie Dornan (also in Valentino) stepping out in his sexy beard and new haircut.
